<h2>Announcing Our New Children's Pastors - Philip &amp; Chanda Hahn</h2><div id="sermon-info" class="sermon"><ul class="sermon-buttons"></ul><!-- .sermon-buttons --><p class="sermon-meta">Posted Nov 30th, 2011 &nbsp;  </p></div><!-- .sermon --><div id="text"><p>We have searched the nation and are pleased to announce Philip and Chanda Hahn have joined our Pastoral team as our new Children&rsquo;s Pastor!</p>
<p>Philip and Chanda have been Children&rsquo;s Pastor for the last 8 years and come with a wealth of passion and experience for children. Their ministry skills include administrating volunteers, training, teaching, preaching, worship leading, website development, creating and editing video, puppetry, illusions, set construction, piano, guitar, singing, songwriting, writing, curriculum, and most of all loving children.</p>
<p>They have been involved in JBQ, Royal Rangers, Kids Camps, Missionettes/MPact, Sunday School, Kids Choir, Awana, community children&rsquo;s outreaches, Christmas productions, Christian Kids Television, Christian Karate, Royal Family Kids Camp&hellip;and more!</p>
<p>Philip and Chanda have two twin children, Aiden and Ashley, born June 3, 2008. &nbsp;Please join us in giving them a warm Portland Christian Center welcome!</p></div>